cron = doccron.cron('0 10 1 2 * 2020-2030')
next_datetime = datetime.now(tz=tzlocal()).replace(month=2, day=1, hour=10,
    minute=0, second=0, microsecond=0)
while True:
    if (next_datetime.year in range(2020, 2031) and next_datetime.month == 
        2 and next_datetime.day == 1 and next_datetime > datetime.now(tz=
        tzlocal())):
        break
    next_datetime = next_datetime.replace(year=next_datetime.year + 1)
next_schedule = next(cron)
assert isinstance(next_schedule, datetime)
assert next_schedule == next_datetime
